ISSUE #375 - 4th March 2018

Application deployment=2C and building abstractions for developers managin=
g applications=2C appears to be a theme at the moment - with several relat=
ed posts this week. Plus interesting thoughts on operations for serverless=
=2C configuring Jenkins and the business case for adopting devops practice=
s.


